# OpenAPI specs are the committed CI snapshot: scripts/sync-openapi.sh refreshes
# them from the (private) hanzoai/openapi repo locally, but CI cannot clone that
# repo and falls back to these checked-in copies. They are TRACKED, not ignored —
# ignoring them silently drops newly-added services from the snapshot. Re-run the
# sync, then commit the diff so the snapshot stays current.

public/r
